title: Avocado Asparagus Tartine
summary: Avocado Asparagus Tartine is a vegan recipe with 10 servings. One portion of this dish contains about 1g of protein, 4g of fat, and a total of 46 calories. For 44 cents per serving, this recipe covers 4% of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. Several people made this recipe, and 1110 would say it hit the spot. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes approximately 5 minutes. A mixture of a couple of arugula, caraway seeds, sunflower seeds, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so yummy. It works well as an inexpensive hor d'oeuvre. All things considered, we decided this recipe deserves a spoonacular score of 94%. This score is awesome.
